text: Langensendelbach is a municipality in the district of Forchheim in Bavaria in Germany with a population of over 3,100.Bevölkerung: Gemeinden, Stichtage Bayerisches Landesamt für Statistik, accessed 26 July 2021. The village Bräuningshof is a part of Langensendelbach. ==References== Category:Forchheim (district)
